            "Steps": [
                {
                    "Type": "Text",
                    "Label": {
                        "en": "It passed down through the Tudor family, until King James I gave it to the Spanish nobility (below) in the early 1600s",
                        "fr": "Elle se transmit au sein de la famille Tudor, jusqu'à ce que le roi Jacques Ier le donne à la noblesse espagnole (ci-dessous) au début du XVIe siècle",
                        "es": "",
                        "zh": ""
                    }
                },
                {
                    "Type": "Image",
                    "Parameters": {
                        "Width": 750,
                        "Height": 565,
                        "Source": "Internal",
                        "Path": "/museums/britishmuseum/sequenceimages/treatyoflondon.jpg"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "Type": "Text",
                    "Label": {
                        "en": "Since the English and Spanish were warring at the time, this was almost certainly as an attempt to soothe relations!",
                        "fr": "Les Anglais et les Espagnols étant en guerre à l'époque, il s'agissait sûrement d'une tentative d'apaisement des relations !",
                        "es": "",
                        "zh": ""
